    "This enables the generated descriptions to focus on the key parts of the image and describe them more accurately.",
    "Ablation ExperimentsOur approach has two main innovations: First, in the image encoder module, CLIP is adopted as the feature extractor with frozen model parameters, and the CLIP model is fine-tuned by inserting an adapter layer.This enables learning new features from fewer traffic scene samples.",
    "Second, a novel WGA-Pooling layer is proposed in the image captioning module to replace the traditional multi-head self-attention layer, reducing model parameters while maintaining performance.",
